parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat adjuster rail can cause the seat to move forward and backward unexpectedly, which can lead to accidents, loss of control, or distraction while driving.
symptoms: The seat moves back and forth while driving
the seat jolts forward when braking
the seat lurches forward/backwards on the seat tracks
the seat moves without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power seat switch can cause the seat to malfunction, leading to unexpected movements or failure to adjust properly.
symptoms: The power seat switch fails to operate
the seat does not adjust properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical interference in the wiring harness can cause the airbag light to illuminate, which may lead to airbag failure in the event of an accident, potentially resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: Airbag light is constantly illuminated
electrical issues with the safety restraint system
loss of head lights
instrument cluster
and turn signals.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failure can cause a loss of critical vehicle functions, such as headlights, instrument cluster, and turn signals, which can increase the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-visibility conditions.
symptoms: Loss of headlights
instrument cluster
and turn signals
electrical issues with the safety restraint system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine failure can cause a loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, and potentially result in fires, which can cause serious injury or death.
symptoms: Fire started under the hood while driving
no indicator lights displayed
no odor of raw fuel was apparent.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The separation of the rear subframe from the differential can cause the drivetrain to hang off the vehicle or rip out of the trunk, leading to loss of control, accidents, or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Popped spot welds in the trunk
cracked differential ear bracket
drivetrain hanging off the vehicle
or ripping out of the trunk.
